  "instructions": [
    "Heat a splash of olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, carrot, and celery; sauté until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the smoked paprika and cook for 30 seconds to release its flavor.",
    "Pour in the turkey stock and bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Add the diced turkey breast, reduce heat, and simmer uncovered for 15–20 minutes until the turkey is cooked through.",
    "Stir in the coconut milk and reduce the heat; let the soup simmer for an additional 5 minutes to meld the flavors.",
    "Add the calamansi juice, kosher salt, and black pepper; adjust seasoning to taste.",
    "Ladle the soup into bowls, garnish with fresh cilantro if desired, and serve hot."
  ],
